{"word":"G2170 - εὐχάριστος - eucháristos - yoo-khar'-is-tos - Thankful","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐχάριστος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eucháristos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-khar'-is-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Thankful</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"நன்றியறிதலுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"mindful of favors, grateful, thankful"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2095 - εὖ - eû - yoo/2095\">G2095</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5483 - χαρίζομαι - charízomai - khar-id'-zom-ahee/5483\">G5483</a>; <i>well favored</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>grateful:</i> - thankful.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2168/2168\">G2168</a>, <a href=\"#/G2169/2169\">G2169</a>, <a href=\"#/G2170/2170\">G2170</a>, <a href=\"#/G4796/4796\">G4796</a>, <a href=\"#/G5463/5463\">G5463</a>, <a href=\"#/G5479/5479\">G5479</a>, <a href=\"#/G5483/5483\">G5483</a>, <a href=\"#/G5484/5484\">G5484</a>, <a href=\"#/G5485/5485\">G5485</a>, <a href=\"#/G5486/5486\">G5486</a>, <a href=\"#/G5487/5487\">G5487</a>, <a href=\"#/G884/884\">G884</a>"}]}